des:
Ego Upgrade will give Alexa a wide range of motivational or confidence inspiring quotes... or maybe something to just make you chuckle.
Need a funny pick me up? Ask for one.
Struggling to find motivation to get something done? This might help.
Need a recipe for a great ganache? Try a different skill, I think this one isn't for you.
